intent.user_query: Which customers made purchases exceeding $5000 in total during 2023?

phases.goal:
Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName, SUM(s.TotalAmount) AS TotalSpent
FROM fitness_db.Customers c
JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID
WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.SaleDate) = 2023
GROUP BY c.CustomerID, c.FirstName, c.LastName
HAVING SUM(s.TotalAmount) > 5000
ORDER BY TotalSpent DESC;

arguments.sql:
